title: Talking with Serena Williams About Her Fall 2017 Collection | HSN
description:
We're making a special visit to Serena Williams' house to get a sneak peek at her new fall fashion collection and talk with her about her fashion inspiration, her thoughts on becoming a mom, and more!

Shop the Serena Williams collection: https://www.hsn.com/shop/serena-williams/6590
